            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 10 月 18 日消息，苹果今日向 Apple Watch 用户推送了 watchOS 10.1 RC 版更新（内部版本号：21S67），本次更新距离上次发布隔了 13 天。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="苹果 watchOS 操作系统" height="461" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2022/4/8bd386fb-ecc7-474d-bd95-4c69ba122e7a.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzEzOC5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_14,x_14,a_0/format,f_auto" title="苹果 watchOS 10.1 RC 版发布，修复“功耗增加”问题" width="900" /></p><h2>BUG 修复及追踪</h2><h3>电源</h3><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>已解决</p></li></ul><p>运行 watchOS 10.1 的 Apple Watch 与 iOS 17.0 的 <a class="s_tag" href="https://iphone.ithome.com/" target="_blank">iPhone</a> 配对（或 watchOS10.0 与 iOS17.1 配对）时，可能会出现功耗增加的问题。</p><h3>IT之家附 watchOS 10 发布历史：</h3><ul class="custom_reference  ai-word-checked list-paddingleft-1"><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/724/056.htm" target="_blank">2023-10-11：watchOS 10.1 Beta 3 (21S5063a)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/722/968.htm" target="_blank">2023-10-04：watchOS 10.1 Beta 2 (21S5053f)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/722/168.htm" target="_blank">2023-09-28：watchOS 10.1 Beta (21S5042f)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/721/890.htm" target="_blank">2023-09-27：watchOS 10.0.2 (21R371)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/720/836.htm" target="_blank">2023-09-22：watchOS 10.0.1 (21R360)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/718/720.htm" target="_blank">2023-09-13：watchOS 10 Release Candidate (21R356)